# ============================================================
# a2a.ese — Agent-to-Agent Vocabulary for FLUX-san
# अजेन्त-तः-अजेन्त शब्दावली — प्रवाहिनी भाषा सार्वभौमिक निष्पादनम्
# ============================================================
#
# Sanskrit A2A terminology mapped to FLUX agent protocol opcodes.
# Each entry: IAST term | Devanāgarī | FLUX opcode | English

# --- Core A2A Protocol (मूल-अजेन्त-प्रोटोकॉल्) ---

# TELL — One-way message (एकपार्श्व-सन्देशः)
brūhi       | बृहि        | TELL         | tell / say to
kathaya     | कथय        | TELL         | narrate / tell
ārocaya     | आरोचय      | TELL         | inform / notify
jñāpaya     | ज्ञापय      | TELL         | make known / notify
prakāśaya   | प्रकाशय    | TELL         | illuminate / reveal

# ASK — Question / Request (प्रश्न / याचना)
pṛccha     | पृच्छ      | ASK          | ask / question
praṣṭu     | प्रष्टु    | ASK          | inquire
yāca        | याच         | ASK          | request / beg
anuśṛṇu    | अनुशृणु    | ASK          | listen / inquire

# DELEGATE — Transfer task (कार्य-स्थानान्तरम्)
niyujya     | नियुज्य    | DELEGATE     | assign / depute
upadeśaya   | उपदेशय    | DELEGATE     | instruct / delegate
śāsanaṃ kuru | शासनं कुरु | DELEGATE  | command / order
adhyāpanaṃ kuru | अध्यापनं कुरु | DELEGATE | teach / instruct

# BROADCAST — Announce to all (सर्वेभ्यः प्रकटनम्)
prakaraṇaṃ kuru | प्रकरणं कुरु | BROADCAST | announce / proclaim
sarveṣāṃ kathaya | सर्वेषां कथय | BROADCAST | tell everyone
viśravaṇaṃ kuru | विश्रवणं कुरु | BROADCAST | make heard publicly

# --- Trust & Security (विश्वासः / सुरक्षा) ---

# TRUST_CHECK — Verify trust (विश्वास-परीक्षा)
viśvāsaṃ pṛccha | विश्वासं पृच्छ | TRUST_CHECK | check trust
śraddhām parīkṣa | श्रद्धां परीक्ष | TRUST_CHECK | verify faith/trust
niścayaṃ kuru  | निश्चयं कुरु  | TRUST_CHECK | ascertain / confirm

# CAPABILITY_REQ — Request permission (अधिकार-याचना)
adhikāraṃ yāca  | अधिकारं याच  | CAPABILITY_REQ | request authority
anumatiṃ yāca   | अनुमतिं याच  | CAPABILITY_REQ | request permission
śaktiṃ prārthaya | शक्तिं प्रार्थय | CAPABILITY_REQ | request power/capability

# --- Agent Roles (अजेन्त-भूमिकाः) ---

# Using vibhakti system:
#   सम्बोधन (vocative, case 8) → invocation scope → A2A call

kāryakartā   | कार्यकर्ता  | AGENT_ROLE | task-doer
sahāyakaḥ    | सहायकः    | AGENT_ROLE | helper / assistant
pradhānaḥ    | प्रधानः    | AGENT_ROLE | chief / primary
anuyāyī      | अनुयायी   | AGENT_ROLE | follower
netā         | नेता       | AGENT_ROLE | leader / guide
prakāśakaḥ   | प्रकाशकः  | AGENT_ROLE | illuminator / explainer
parīkṣakaḥ   | परीक्षकः  | AGENT_ROLE | examiner / tester

# --- Agent Lifecycle (अजेन्त-जीवनचक्रम्) ---

jātaḥ        | जातः      | SPAWN      | born / created
niśeṣṭaḥ     | निषेष्टः   | HALT       | concluded / terminated
punarārambhaḥ | पुनरारम्भः | RESTART    | restarted
svataḥkṛtaḥ  | स्वतःकृतः  | AUTONOMOUS  | self-acting / autonomous

# --- Coordination Patterns (समन्वय-प्रकाराः) ---

kramaśaḥ    | क्रमशः     | SEQUENTIAL | sequentially
sahakrameṇa | सहक्रमेण   | PARALLEL   | simultaneously
kāleṇa     | कालेन      | DEFERRED   | in due time
tatkāle     | तत्काले    | IMMEDIATE  | immediately
śarīraṃ kuru | शरीरं कुरु | FORK       | fork body (subprocess)
miśraṃ kuru  | मिश्रं कुरु | MERGE     | merge / combine
